@robertsoakes 
1. I agree, good point - we need to have a function which converts the Rocket.Chat message into Slack's format. As it needs to be 100% compatible, that's our aim.
2. That is a good point, we will need to implement the pagination at a higher level - inside of the Meteor methods which are called.

